csci331.team.red.shared

Class Character

  • java.lang.Object
    • csci331.team.red.shared.Character

  • public class Character
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains specific game character information, generated from the CharacterDAO.

    CSCI331T MW ENCAPSULATION

    By creating getters and setters for all attributes of the Character class, implementation is hidden from the outside world. This also prevents unwanted access from the outside world

    Game Character Information:
    • Date of Birth
    • Driver's License Number
    • Last Name
    • First Name
    • Passport ID
    • Address
    • City
    • Country
    • Postal Code
    • Occupation
    • Gender
    • PersonPicture
    • Fraud
    Author:
    melany

        CSCI331-TAG MW OVERRIDE

        Another override, this one overrides one of the built-in java methods rather than two methods I've wrote for different classes.
        I overrode this one because the built-in equals doesn't compare a Character object. In addition to overriding the equals method, I also overrode the hashCode in case there is every a hashMap of Characters Instantiated, which is shown below.
